      "title": "Budget today",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "President Ranil Wickramasinghe is going to present the Budget Appropriation Bill to the Parliament today (30th) afternoon.",
        "The Parliament is scheduled to meet today (30th) at 1.00 pm under the chairmanship of Speaker Mahinda Yapa Abeywardena and the President's budget speech will also begin at that time."
